I try to slurp it up from the plane window
the pink
and the passing grey
but every five minutes I’m back at it again
pulling twigs out of my broomstick
sinking my feelings into a sandwich
and I could go up and up and up
make a pile of twigs so high
my toes would get pricked
my nose would get perked
by the passing grey
but every five minutes I’m back at it again
sinking my legs into the cockpit
sapping my neighbor with treacle
skipping to the next song
with my tongue stuck out to lap up the
